{"tid":1907994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[咩邏輯?]林鄭月娥：內地抵港強制檢疫人士增　說明不能完全封關","createTime":"2020-03-03T03:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T03:58:57.000Z","uid":57582,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5a6fc5ec06ae47c650ed1d8b7655508fbde714","tid":1907994,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，當局早前推出強制檢疫措施，從內地抵港的人士要在家居強制檢疫14日，這類人士數字趨升，即是有不少人因各種原因，即使回港後要在家隔離14日都要回來，亦解釋了為何不能完全不准出入香港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，要感謝大量公務員、退休人員及義工，加入支援家居檢疫工作的行列，至今仍可承受目前趨升的人數。<br />\n<br />\n她說，由她領導的督導委員會暨指揮中心，會不斷按疫情調整應對措施，當局亦因此無法分心處理其他本來想做的工作，希望疫情穩定下來後，全港會齊心協助重整香港經濟。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512158-20200303.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512158-20200303.htm&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=64eeb4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512158-20200303.htm&h=f9694162\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512158-20200303.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n強制檢疫下入境數字仍然趨升<br />\n代表強制檢疫措施無效<br />\n亦解釋了為何需要完全封關<br />\n<br />\n其實點講都通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbe1785f830814657624067b2f675c183ae6511","tid":1907994,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:30:35.000Z","msg":"因為班支那豬要黎播毒<br />\n所以唔可以封關阻止"},{"pid":"fc982ad3fff26593cc8f722c12077b2132c32eb0","tid":1907994,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"緊係上升啦，一次on site check都無，鳩流流"},{"pid":"c47dd71886b8009e32af0e28054a0a67643d64ca","tid":1907994,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"封左吙唔洗檢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d290eb5ddbd4a8768fcc35f592fab6f56c248ef8","tid":1907994,"ui